column2: b'SKET Dance: Imouto no Nayami ni Nayamu Ani ni Nayamu Imouto to Sono Nakama-tachi'
b'An OVA of SKET Dance bundled with the 29th volume of the manga, covering chapters 198, 199, and 200.\n\nThis is a conclusion of some of the events shown in the last episode of the anime series.'
